y consistent with the\nphotoionization radius. The results may be explained in terms of a \"failed\nwind\" like those predicted in some numerical simulations. We discuss our\nresults in the context of accretion flows across the mass scale, and the\npotential role of failed winds in black hole state transitions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jun 2013 18:14:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Apr 2014 19:00:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
