ly,\nwe estimate the goodness of the applied methodology and we confirm that the\nstochastic approach must be considered for a correct description of the ant\nfighting dynamics. With respect to other war models, our chemical one considers\nall phases of the battle and not only casualties. Thus, we can count on more\nexperimental data, but we also have more parameters to fit. In any case, our\nmodel allows a much more detailed description of the fights.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Jun 2013 11:13:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 29 Nov 2013 12:49:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 6 May 2016 12:44:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-05-09"}
