cted. For a more detailed analysis, we also studied the vehicle dynamics at\na microscopic level and provide a comparison of real detector data with\nsimulated data of the identical highway segment.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Jun 2013 14:20:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Jul 2013 06:45:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-07-08"}
